<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Missions_of_India">Missions of India</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Paris_Foreign_Missions_Society&amp;action=edit&amp;section=26" title="Edit section: Missions of India"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
